[201710]="Pone una trampa que ralentiza un 80 % a los enemigos en un radio de 8 metros cada 2 segundos y emite un pulso cada 3 segundos. Inflige 150 de daño por pulso. Dura 12 segundos.",
[201726]="<<1>> brands the earth underneath them with a rune of protection for <<2>>. Standing within the rune reduces the damage they and their allies take by <<3>>. \r\n\r\nIf the attacker is an Undead, Daedra, or Werewolf the rune reduces damage taken by an additional <<4>>.",
