[227332]="Violently drain the last spark of life from a corpse, dealing <<1>> over <<2>> to all enemies around the corpse and between you and the corpse.  \r\n\r\nIf the siphon lasts its full duration it causes the corpse to explode, dealing an additional <<3>> to all enemies around the corpse.  This ability scales off your highest offensive stats.\r\n\r\nWhile slotted, your damage done is increased by <<4>>.",
[227334]="Violently drain the last spark of life from a corpse, dealing <<1>> over <<2>> to all enemies around the corpse and between you and the corpse.  \r\n\r\nIf the siphon lasts its full duration it causes the corpse to explode, dealing an additional <<3>> to all enemies around the corpse.  This ability scales off your highest offensive stats.\r\n\r\nWhile slotted, your damage done is increased by <<4>>.",
[227381]="Cuando infliges daño con una habilidad de arcanista, se aplican dos efectos de estado aleatorios al objetivo y se genera un crux. Este efecto se puede producir una vez cada <<1>>. Infligir daño con una habilidad de Emisario del Tomo reduce la reutilización en <<2>>, hasta una vez cada <<3>>.\r\n\r\nAumenta un <<4>> el daño infligido con efectos de estado.",
